title: Rare Hits Of The 80's Vol 73
description:
Welcome to part 73 of this beloved 80's obscure compilation! On this instalment, I have thrown in hand picked selection of cool darkwave, post punk, synth & gothwave tunes. So just when you thought this series couldn't get any more obscure! 
Enjoy & seed fellows.
